task.summary: I've changed the IDE I use
Rearranged codes, added integer 'less than' comparator
Transformed the native implementation part of stdlib to a dynamic library.
Added Command-line interface. You now need to set ERABLE_LIB to ERABLE_BIN to sth like /usr/local/lib.The usage of command 'ErableVM' : ErableVM [-f file]
Modified License of ErableVM/include/dynamicro.cpp.Sorry for not putting the right license
Renamed ErableVM to ErableLang. Extracted cpp and hpp files for ErableVM to a unique ErableLang/VM directory.
Moved math.cpp and math.hpp to ErableLang/stdlib/
Decreased Minimum CMake Version again (For tanpero)
